  From Center: 1.000000
  From Right: 1.000000

Move Right (B[:,:,1]):
Current→Next   Left   Center  Right
Left         0.050   0.950   0.000
Center       0.000   0.050   0.950
Right        0.000   0.000   1.000
Column sums for Move Right:
  From Left: 1.000000
  From Center: 1.000000
  From Right: 1.000000

💎 3. PREFERENCES (C vector) - PyMDP obj_array format
======================================================================
Vector shape: (3,)
Interpretation: log P(observation preferred)
Higher values = more preferred observations

